AND EVASION ARE IMPORTANT,

4
00:00:30,322 --> 00:00:32,241
AND TIME WAS, IF YOU
ROCKED THOSE TWO THINGS,

5
00:00:32,282 --> 00:00:35,285
IT'S ALL YOU NEEDED
TO BE THE BEST.

6
00:00:35,327 --> 00:00:36,286
'TIL NOW, THAT IS.

7
00:00:36,328 --> 00:00:37,913
YEAH, HATE TO SAY IT,

8
00:00:37,955 --> 00:00:39,831
