LIKE THAT ANYMORE.

9
00:00:39,873 --> 00:00:41,583
IN FACT, I GOT A MESSAGE
FOR THE FOLKS

10
00:00:41,625 --> 00:00:43,252
WHO SPENT
THE LAST EIGHT MONTHS INDOORS

11
00:00:43,293 --> 00:00:45,796
BOOSTING THEIR AGI.

12
00:00:45,837 --> 00:00:48,298
