14
00:00:51,176 --> 00:00:53,011
Moderator: NOW THAT'S THE KIND
OF COMMENT WE'D EXPECT

15
00:00:53,053 --> 00:00:55,138
FROM THE TOP PLAYER
OF "GUN GALE ONLINE,"

16
00:00:55,180 --> 00:00:57,516
ONE OF THE MOST
CHALLENGING VRMMOs!

17
00:00:57,557 --> 00:00:59,309
TALK ABOUT CONTROVERSIAL!

18
00:00:59,351 --> 00:01:00,602
XeXeeD: I GUESS,
BUT WHO KNOWS

19
00:01:00,644 --> 00:01:02,229
IF I'LL BE
ON "MMO STREAM" AGAIN,

20
00:01:02,271 --> 00:01:03,981
SO MIGHT AS WELL STIR THINGS UP!

21
00:01:04,022 --> 00:01:06,400
Moderator: OH, PLEASE!
SO, DO YOU THINK YOU HAVE A SHOT

22
00:01:06,441 --> 00:01:07,901
