I COULD WIN IT!

25
00:01:12,197 --> 00:01:14,116
Crowd: (BOOING)

26
00:01:14,157 --> 00:01:16,743
Yamikaze: IT WON'T BE
THAT EASY, XEXEED.

27
00:01:16,785 --> 00:01:19,621
THE B. o. B.'S A SOLO TOURNEY,
SO IT'S WAY DIFFERENT.

28
00:01:19,663 --> 00:01:22,916
