DOESN'T MEAN IT'LL WORK AGAIN.

29
00:01:22,958 --> 00:01:26,253
IF I WERE YOU, I WOULDN'T CHALK
MY WINS UP TO MY STATUS TYPE.

30
00:01:26,295 --> 00:01:28,422
XeXeeD: YEAH, WELL,
IF ANYTHING, MY RESULTS

31
00:01:28,463 --> 00:01:31,508
