HAPPENIN' IN "GGO."

32
00:01:31,550 --> 00:01:33,552
YOU'RE ALL ABOUT AGI, YAMIKAZE.

33
00:01:33,594 --> 00:01:35,429
GO FIGURE YOU'D BE IN DENIAL.

34
00:01:35,470 --> 00:01:36,471
Yamikaze: (GROANS)

35
00:01:36,513 --> 00:01:38,307
XeXeeD: WAKE UP, PEOPLE!

36
00:01:38,348 --> 00:01:41,351
'TIL NOW, THE BEST STRATEGY
WAS BOOSTING YOUR AGI

37
00:01:41,393 --> 00:01:43,895
AND SHOOTING A POWERFUL GUN
AS FAST AS YOU COULD,

38
00:01:43,937 --> 00:01:45,480
BUT THE REALITY IS,

39
00:01:45,522 --> 00:01:48,275
THE BALANCE OF GAME PLAY
IN AN MMO IS ALWAYS CHANGING,

40
00:01:48,317 --> 00:01:49,943
ESPECIALLY IN GAMES
LIKE THIS ONE,

41
00:01:49,985 --> 00:01:52,612
WITH LEVELS THAT DON'T LET YOU
RE‐SPEC YOUR STATS.

42
00:01:52,654 --> 00:01:56,158
YOU HAVE TO THINK AHEAD AND BE
SMART WHEN USING YOUR POINTS,

43
00:01:56,199 --> 00:01:58,243
'CAUSE THE BEST WEAPON
IN ONE LEVEL ZONE,

44
00:01:58,285 --> 00:02:00,078
MIGHT NOT WORK FOR YOU
IN THE NEXT.

45
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,456
BESIDES, THE NEW GUNS COMIN' OUT

46
00:02:02,497 --> 00:02:04,416
