52
00:02:15,594 --> 00:02:17,429
Players: (MURMURING)

53
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:23,477
Player #3: YOU'RE NOTHING
BUT A FAKE, XEXEED,

54
00:02:23,518 --> 00:02:27,522
