IN THE END

58
00:02:45,874 --> 00:02:49,753
IS THE PLAYER'S ABILITY TO‐‐
(GASPING)

59
00:02:57,427 --> 00:02:58,762
Moderator: UH‐OH.

60
00:02:58,804 --> 00:03:01,014
I GUESS WE HAVE
A BAD CONNECTION HERE.

61
00:03:01,056 --> 00:03:03,517
DON'T WORRY, FOLKS.
I'M SURE HE'LL BE BACK SHORTLY.

62
00:03:03,558 --> 00:03:06,978
STAY TUNED
FOR MORE "MMO STREAM."

63
00:03:08,188 --> 00:03:10,023
Players: (GASPING)

64
00:03:10,065 --> 00:03:13,860
Player #3: THIS IS REAL POWER,
REAL STRENGTH!

65
00:03:13,902 --> 00:03:18,240
LET YOUR FEAR CARVE
ONE NAME INTO YOUR BRAINS...

66
00:03:18,281 --> 00:03:20,826
THE NAME I SHARE
WITH THIS WEAPON...

67
00:03:20,867 --> 00:03:22,828
DEATH GUN!

68
00:03:42,472 --> 00:03:45,767
Asuna: DECEMBER SEVENTH, 2025.

69
00:03:45,809 --> 00:03:48,395
HAS IT ALREADY BEEN A YEAR?

70
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:55,527
(GASPS)

71
00:03:57,237 --> 00:04:01,616
