IS BETWEEN THE REAL WORLD...

72
00:04:01,658 --> 00:04:02,659
AND THE VIRTUAL.

73
00:04:03,994 --> 00:04:05,829
Kirito: THE AMOUNT OF DATA.
THAT'S ALL.

74
00:04:05,871 --> 00:04:08,248
Asuna: (GASPS)

75
