YOU SCARED ME.

76
00:04:10,041 --> 00:04:11,501
Kirito: SORRY 'BOUT THAT.

77
00:04:11,543 --> 00:04:12,586
I'M ON TIME, THOUGH.

78
00:04:12,627 --> 00:04:14,087
(GIGGLES) WHAT?

79
00:04:14,129 --> 00:04:15,338
Asuna: (GIGGLES)

80
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:17,424
NO, I'M SORRY.
I WAS SPACING OUT.

81
00:04:17,466 --> 00:04:18,675
ANYWAY...

82
00:04:18,717 --> 00:04:21,386
HELLO, KIRITO.
HOW ARE YOU DOING TODAY?!

83
00:04:21,428 --> 00:04:25,766
Kirito: IT'S BEEN GOOD SO FAR,
BUT IT'S EVEN BETTER NOW.

84
00:04:25,807 --> 00:04:27,642
Asuna: WHAT ARE YOU STARING AT?

85
00:04:27,684 --> 00:04:29,978
Kirito: NOTHING! JUST...

86
