87
00:04:31,855 --> 00:04:33,899
IT BRINGS BACK
A LOT OF MEMORIES.

88
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:35,817
Asuna: I GUESS IT DOES.

89
00:04:35,859 --> 00:04:37,652
NO RAPIER, THOUGH.

90
00:04:37,694 --> 00:04:40,697
LOOKS LIKE YOU WENT OVERBOARD
ON THE BLACK TODAY.

91
00:04:40,739 --> 00:04:42,115
Kirito: YEAH!

92
00:04:42,157 --> 00:04:44,201
SUGU THREW EVERYTHING
IN THE WASH THIS MORNING,

93
00:04:44,242 --> 00:04:45,660
AND THIS IS ALL I HAD LEFT.

94
00:04:45,702 --> 00:04:47,746
Asuna: THEN STOP
PUTTING YOUR LAUNDRY OFF.

95
00:04:47,788 --> 00:04:50,290
‐ Kirito: (SIGHS)
‐ Asuna: (LAUGHS)

96
00:04:50,332 --> 00:04:53,585
I CAN'T BELIEVE WE BOTH
DRESSED IN OUR OLD COLORS TODAY.

97
00:04:53,627 --> 00:04:55,420
