186
00:08:53,533 --> 00:08:54,909
Kikuoka: HEY, KIRITO!

187
00:08:54,951 --> 00:08:56,911
OVER HERE! (CHUCKLING)

188
00:09:04,335 --> 00:09:06,421
Kikuoka: GO AHEAD.
ORDER WHATEVER YOU WANT.

189
00:09:06,463 --> 00:09:08,048
IT'S ON ME.

190
00:09:08,089 --> 00:09:10,050
Kirito: THANK YOU, SIR.
THAT'S VERY KIND OF YOU.

191
00:09:10,091 --> 00:09:12,677
Kikuoka: COME ON. YOU DON'T
HAVE TO BE SO FORMAL WITH ME.

192
00:09:12,719 --> 00:09:15,180
