(GASPS)

196
00:09:22,812 --> 00:09:25,690
(GROANS)

197
00:09:25,732 --> 00:09:28,651
I'D LIKE
THE PARFAIT AU CHOCOLAT,

198
00:09:28,693 --> 00:09:30,904
THE FRAMBOISE MILLE‐FEUILLE,

199
00:09:30,945 --> 00:09:32,530
AND A HAZELNUT LATTE.

200
00:09:34,032 --> 00:09:35,116
‐ (SIGHS)
‐ Kikuoka: SORRY TO MAKE YOU

201
00:09:35,158 --> 00:09:36,826
