IN THE HOSPITAL, REMEMBER?

209
00:09:50,924 --> 00:09:52,550
Kirito: (SIGHS)

210
00:09:52,592 --> 00:09:55,720
Kirito: HE'S RIGHT.
WHEN I CAME TO,

211
00:09:55,762 --> 00:09:58,014
