SECTION.

216
00:10:10,568 --> 00:10:12,570
Kikuoka: (HUMMING)

217
00:10:13,947 --> 00:10:16,032
Kirito: SO WHAT'D YOU
WANNA SEE ME ABOUT?

218
00:10:16,074 --> 00:10:17,700
IF IT'S ANYTHING
"S. A. O." RELATED,

